Introduction

This document shows the space usage over the last year on each production data server:

  • DCICHISQL1
  • DCICHISQL2
  • DCICORSQL3
  • DCICORSQL4
  • DCICORSQL85

It looks at the used space by each database file for the three largest database files:

  • mis_db
  • darwin_db
  • dialysis_db

NOTE: All sizes are in GB.
